file.string:
Steps to use this app: 
 1. Pair your band with the phone
 2. Make sure Microsoft Health is installed
 3. Give the application permission to access your heart rate data by pressing the Heart Rate Consent button and then pressing yes on the dialog that pops up.
 4. Press the Start button
 5. Data from the heart rate sensor should be displayed.
